; PULL, All ranks         BRI                   1
INumber 960
Name 318
WORN_DON
ARMOR
EQUAL ITEMADJ1 145
EQUAL ITEMADJ2 1130
IFPREVERB2 EXAM -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You sense the goodness of the power inhabiting the aura.
  IFVAR INTNUM3 = 1
    ECHO PLAYER **GM EYES ONLY**
    ECHO PLAYER This amulet is crafted for members of the Shemri Church only.
    ECHO PLAYER Set VAL5 to the rank of the member. This is a number from one to five.
    ECHO PLAYER Cartin Greycloak and Jacqueline are the two people who are rank 5.
    ECHO PLAYER They alone can set ranks in the Church at this time.
    ECHO PLAYER As there is a ritual to both create amulets and promote people
    ECHO PLAYER There are few reasons for a GM to be asked for one. Instead send them
    ECHO PLAYER to the temple elders.
  ENDIF
ENDIF
