*DESCRIPTION_START
This austere, north-south hallway is lit with small sconces that seem
to have a hint of incense in them. An opening leads into the courtyard
at the heart of the Church. An oak door with an oak tree symbol is at
north end of the hall, opposite a maple door.
*DESCRIPTION_END
