ITEM 3 1112
EXTEND 3 that reads "Knights Area closed for extensive purification."
IFPREVERB GO 0
        IFCARRY 960 145
                IFITEM -1 WORN
                        GMMSG %N went in the Shemri door.
                        ECHO PLAYER A large, benevolent acolyte glances at your Church Pin and allows you to pass.
                        ECHO OTHERS % walks past a large, peaceful acolyte and enters the chamber.
                        IFVAR ITEMVAL5 < 3
                                DISBAND
                        ENDIF
                ELSE
                        ECHO PLAYER A large, apologetic acolyte says "I'm sorry, you need to be wearing a Church Pin to go in here."
                        CLEARVERB
                ENDIF
        ELSE
                ECHO PLAYER A large apologetic acolyte says "I'm sorry, you need to be wearing a Church Pin to go in here."
                GMMSG %N was refused entry to the Shemri door.
                CLEARVERB
        ENDIF
